---
title: BBQ Chicken Sandwiches with Potato Coins and Chive Ranch
description: Enjoy BBQ cookout flavours in a speedy chicken sammie! Cutting the potatoes into no-fuss coins makes this recipe extra quick.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwichs-au-poulet-bbq-3b113ff3-79bf2424.jpg
